Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上的波濤聲 比平時更加清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炫目的月光充滿了天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那月光如此溫暖地 擁抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 若能盡情享受世界給我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 新威尼斯的秋天快要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很快就要迎來寒冬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛麗絲先行成為正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的共同練習已經變成了與藍華兩個人的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華啊 開始變冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩個人的共同練習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是讓人想起我們剛剛相識的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在說完全不寂寞是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是非常值得高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們也不能輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一起為了成為正式領航員努力吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能再跟妳一起共同練習了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要道歉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是一直努力著 夢想著這一天的到來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳晉級為正式領航員 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…我就知道燈里會這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一件事想跟妳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.79,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那片 蔚藍的大海與風…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 藍華她晉級為正式領航員了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是個好消息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱號是Rozen Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薔薇女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定下來是那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃一直都在煩惱這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候進行藍華的晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為藍華不僅僅是要成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還要背負整個姬屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果是藍華的話一定不會有問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 我還有一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑塔·露琪亞附近要開一家姬屋的分店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,440)\fs20}Santa Lucia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華要到那裡擔任分店長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她說以後會變得很忙很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是件值得高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華卻哭得很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天將對妳進行正式領航員晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在好緊張哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我終於要面對晉級考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為實在緊張得睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雖然是晚上 我還是出去練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 終於等到這一天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長 謝謝你陪我出來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 就跟平時練習一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了 不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛從中學的同學會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就弄丟錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明牢牢繫在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 鬢子妳這麼晚在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…是我的正式領航員晉級考試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺最近也要進行晉級考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常瞭解鬢子妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 曉 我找到你的錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？在哪找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你掉在店裡的洗手間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…居然在那種怎麼都不可能掉的地方掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭錢包 你給我去廁所睡覺吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 曉 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？燈里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼晚還在練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬢子啊 考試加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望天氣不要變壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得努力睡一覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遠方的天空很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午應該就放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晉級考試…不如延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新選一個天氣好的日子再考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直等著這一天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是艾莉西亞前輩決定給我考試的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天對於我來說 已經很重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是下午也一直下的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備工作都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱水袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真體貼的服務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位和毯子都暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡到大運河之間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從任何一個地方都能遙望大鐘樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 雨過天晴之後我最推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這條小路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是賽艇的選手先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的船槳都是自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的路要由自己來闖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 就會留下遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年我要奪冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於到了大運河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(515,440)\fs20}Canal Grande
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新威尼斯的版圖上畫出一個倒S型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大運河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您冷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是橫跨大運河的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里亞托橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是水上通行之人與橋上眺望之人邂逅的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉 她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 伍迪 我們按計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hurray～ hurray～ 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}hurray～ hurray～ 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}加油啊 燈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曉先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞小姐也要加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快給我下來 小心掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖馬可廣場和被稱為Lagoon的瀉湖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不斷變換著色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被溫暖的顏色所環抱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在其中不斷被治癒一樣不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 操縱鳳尾舟的技巧和導遊詞都很熟練了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還能感覺到燈里獨特的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…非常重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 這條水路…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 平時是禁止新人進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在我們可以進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著水路盡頭的 燈里的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前任何一條水路都要窄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還有這樣的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不可思議地 感覺不到慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人總是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從船槳傳達到指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃而靜謐的 水的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與大家度過的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撐著現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有力地推動著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳尾舟要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里 這次的鳳尾舟之旅太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠靜而恬然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像鳳尾舟與海水融合在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這是最後的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始的路線由燈里妳來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成為怎樣的正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要由燈里自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成為怎樣的正式領航員嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事物即將有所轉變之時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都踏上了屬於自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像相互催發著對方的變化一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連鎖重疊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切 從最初都已經被命運所決定一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要成為的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像祖母那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像艾莉西亞前輩這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像亞利亞公司一樣的領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從妳來到AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的世界就翻開了新的一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都開始閃爍著迷人的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人施展了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像溫柔地環抱著AQUA的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延伸到無盡遠方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空與大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與妳相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的海藍寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,440)\fs20}Aquamarine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海藍…寶石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深邃的…藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳晉級成為正式領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 我是正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一直…都憧憬著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從踏足這顆星球那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件重要的事情要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷變換的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恬靜溫馨的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我將啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.65,0:24:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.91,0:24:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 嶄新的開端…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.58,0:24:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
