Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:57.18,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓人陶醉的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.45,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩渦
